cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a neural network model for learning an abstract description of shared physical dynamics in visually different environments. This involves multi-task learning, which is a common topic in the machine learning community and falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with visual stimuli and recognition. Additionally, the paper discusses the ability of agents to make decisions and take actions, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper involves neural networks (cs.NE) as the proposed model is a type of neural network.
